---
title: Seared Duck & Cherry Red Wine Jus with Twice-Cooked Potatoes, Roasted Garlic & Orange Salad
description: ‘Tis the season for indulging, and we’ve got just the meal for it! Perfectly seared duck is paired with a rich and sweet cherry red wine jus, delivering depth and warmth with every bite. Accompanied by crispy-on-the-outside, fluffy-on-the-inside potatoes and
a vibrant orange salad, this dish is true celebration of holiday flavours.
